GSD.description:
media: coda: Add check for kmalloc

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v4.9.337 by commit d308c4a035b636756786af91e5f39f9d92d7d42a, it was introduced in version v3.19 by commit cb1d3a336371e35c3920cc50a701c5403c255644. For more details please see the references link.
